# Mosoro v1.5 ACL - Least Privilege

user gateway
topic readwrite mosoro/v1/#

user api
topic read mosoro/v1/agents/+/status
topic read mosoro/v1/agents/+/events
topic read mosoro/v1/traffic/#
topic write mosoro/v1/admin/#

user agent-locus-001
topic write mosoro/v1/agents/locus-001/#
topic read mosoro/v1/agents/locus-001/commands
topic read mosoro/v1/traffic/#

pattern readwrite mosoro/v1/agents/%c/#
pattern read mosoro/v1/traffic/#

topic deny #
